In [27]:
Sleep['In Bed Time'] = [int(x.split(':')[0])*60+int(x.split(':')[1]) for x in Sleep['In Bed Time']]
Sleep['In Bed Time'] = [x-24*60 if x>20*60 else x for x in Sleep['In Bed Time']]

Sleep['Out Bed Time'] = [int(x.split(':')[0])*60+int(x.split(':')[1]) for x in Sleep['Out Bed Time']]
Sleep['Out Bed Time'] = [x-24*60 if x>20*60 else x  for x in Sleep['Out Bed Time']]

Sleep['Onset Time'] = [int(x.split(':')[0])*60+int(x.split(':')[1])for x in Sleep['Onset Time']]
Sleep['Onset Time'] = [x-24*60 if x>20*60 else x  for x in Sleep['Onset Time']]

Sleep = Sleep.fillna(0)

# Line plot of Cortisol and Melatonin concentrations obtained from saliva sample. Differencebetween “before sleep” and “wake up” hormones concentration

f,ax = plt.subplots(1,2,figsize=(10,5))
for w,c in zip(['Before_Sleep','WakeUp'],['g','r']):
    df_w = Saliva[Saliva['Sample']==w]
    df_w = df_w[df_w['Cortisol NORM']<0.1]
    ax[0].scatter([w]*len(df_w), df_w['Cortisol NORM'], c=c, label=w, edgecolors='k', s=100, alpha=0.8)
ax[0].set_title('(c) Cortisol',fontsize=25)
ax[0].set_ylabel('$\mu g$ Cortisol / 100 $\mu g$ Protein',fontsize=15)
ax[0].set_xlabel('')
plt.sca(ax[0])
plt.xlim(-0.2,1.2)
plt.ylim(0,0.10)

for w,c in zip(['Before_Sleep','WakeUp'],['g','r']):
    df_w = Saliva[Saliva['Sample']==w]
    df_w = df_w[df_w['Melatonin NORM']<2.5e-8]
    ax[1].scatter([w]*len(df_w), df_w['Melatonin NORM'],c=c, edgecolors='k', s=100, alpha=0.8)
ax[1].set_title('(d) Melatonin',fontsize=25)
ax[1].set_ylabel('$\mu g$ Melatonin / $\mu g$ Protein',fontsize=15)
ax[1].set_xlabel('')
plt.sca(ax[1])
plt.xlim(-0.2,1.2)
plt.ylim(0,2.5e-8)

f.tight_layout()
plt.show()
